
            Video
            BBC caller asks Theresa May for honest referendum answer
            Prime Minister Theresa May takes calls on the BBC News Channel and BBC Radio 5 Live in a special programme presented by Emma Barnett.Michael asked her: "What in your honest opinion is better for the UK, your deal or the deal we had if we stayed in the EU?".
                
                        23 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
